      "startTime": 323.7999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "コホン……い、今はタコさんの話は置いておいてですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahem… a-anyway‚ let's put the sausage talk aside.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 328.0711695184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "私一人だとどうしても根を詰めちゃうので、みんなに\n無理してたら止めるからねって言われてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I'm on my own I tend to overdo it‚ so everyone told me\nthey'll stop me if I push too far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.4333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "タコさん目当てに帰ると思われてるところは\n子供扱いされてるみたいで、釈然としませんけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But thinking I'd only go back for sausages—\nit feels like I'm being treated like a kid‚ which I don't like…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.8999885559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "……俺が心配するまでもなかったな\nそうだよな、琴乃には月ストのみんなもいるんだもんな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Seems I didn't need to worry after all.\nRight—Kotono‚ you've got all of Moon Tempest with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.9666552226,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
