      "text": "いえ、これまでのことを考えると\n心配されても仕方ないですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ considering how I've been so far‚\nit's only natural to be worried about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.6333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "ま、みんなもこう言ってることだし\n寮から乗り込んでくる前に、今日は帰った方がいいぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ since everyone's saying that‚\nyou'd better head back before they storm the studio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.4333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_10_02-ktn030.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、そうします\n帰ったら帰ったで、なんかお説教されそうですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right‚ I'll do that.\nThough once I get back‚ I'll probably get lectured…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 375.1333218892,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
